<number box="[1320,1336,151,175]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" value="4.0">4</number>
). Mandible. (Fig. 
<number box="[259,272,188,212]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" value="3.0">3</number>
C) with 
<number box="[365,379,188,212]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" value="6.0">6</number>
large distinct teeth, apical two smaller and outer margin with 
<number box="[1074,1101,188,212]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" value="11.0">11</number>
denticules.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,151,1193]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">
Thorax. Scutum brown, with dark brown caudal and lateral margin; scutellum dark brown with 
<number box="[1310,1338,223,247]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" value="18.0">18</number>
bristles; postscutellum and pleuron brown. Legs. (Figs. 
<number box="[680,692,260,284]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" value="3.0">3</number>
D–F) Coxae brown; trochanter pale; fore femur yellow at the base with a broad, dark brown middle band and dark brown apex, fore femur with 
<number box="[1045,1073,295,319]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" value="12.0">12</number>
(
<number box="[1090,1162,295,319]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" value="12.5" valueMax="13.0" valueMin="12.0">12–13</number>
