</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,151,1193]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">
Abdomen. Tergites chocolate colored with dark lateral margin, setae scattered, sparse, segment VIII with a tuft of caudolateral setae, pleural membrane pale and cerci brown. Spermathecae. (Fig. 
<number box="[1083,1096,769,793]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" value="3.0">3</number>
J) highly sclerotized, rounded, rudimentary third present.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,151,1193]" box="[201,391,841,866]" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">Male. Unknown.</paragraph>
